@Rebet.API_HostAddress = http://localhost:5189
@Token = 

### ============================================
### AUTHENTICATION
### ============================================

### Login (use any seeded user: user1@test.com through user200@test.com, password: Test123!)
POST {{Rebet.API_HostAddress}}/api/v1/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "user1@test.com",
  "password": "Test123!"
}

### Register New User
POST {{Rebet.API_HostAddress}}/api/v1/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "newuser@test.com",
  "password": "SecurePass123!",
  "firstName": "New",
  "lastName": "User",
