### ============================================
### EVENTS (No Auth Required)
### ============================================

### Get All Events
GET {{Rebet.API_HostAddress}}/api/v1/events?page=1&pageSize=20
Accept: application/json

### Get Events by Sport
GET {{Rebet.API_HostAddress}}/api/v1/events?sport=Football&page=1&pageSize=20
Accept: application/json

### Get Events by League
GET {{Rebet.API_HostAddress}}/api/v1/events?league=Premier League&page=1&pageSize=20
Accept: application/json

### Get Events by Status
GET {{Rebet.API_HostAddress}}/api/v1/events?status=Scheduled&page=1&pageSize=20
Accept: application/json

### Get Event by ID (replace {eventId} with actual ID)
GET {{Rebet.API_HostAddress}}/api/v1/events/{eventId}
Accept: application/json

### ============================================
### EXPERTS (No Auth Required)
### ============================================

### Get All Experts
GET {{Rebet.API_HostAddress}}/api/v1/experts?page=1&pageSize=20
Accept: application/json

### Get Experts by Tier
GET {{Rebet.API_HostAddress}}/api/v1/experts?tier=Gold&page=1&pageSize=20
Accept: application/json

### Get Experts by Specialization
GET {{Rebet.API_HostAddress}}/api/v1/experts?specialization=Football&page=1&pageSize=20
Accept: application/json

### Get Expert by ID (replace {expertId} with actual ID)
GET {{Rebet.API_HostAddress}}/api/v1/experts/{expertId}
Accept: application/json

### ============================================
### POSITIONS (Auth Required)
### ============================================

### Get All Positions
GET {{Rebet.API_HostAddress}}/api/v1/positions?page=1&pageSize=20
Authorization: Bearer {{Token}}
Accept: application/json

### Get Positions by Expert
GET {{Rebet.API_HostAddress}}/api/v1/positions?expertId={expertId}&page=1&pageSize=20
Authorization: Bearer {{Token}}
Accept: application/json

### Get Position by ID
GET {{Rebet.API_HostAddress}}/api/v1/positions/{positionId}
Authorization: Bearer {{Token}}
Accept: application/json

### Create Position (replace with actual eventId)
POST {{Rebet.API_HostAddress}}/api/v1/positions
Authorization: Bearer {{Token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "sportEventId": "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000",
  "market": "Match Result",
  "selection": "Home Win",
  "odds": 2.50,
  "analysis": "Strong home team advantage based on recent form"
}

### Vote on Position
POST {{Rebet.API_HostAddress}}/api/v1/positions/{positionId}/vote
Authorization: Bearer {{Token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "type": "Upvote"
}

